comments: Gay's (SAS) forearm makes clean contact with the ball to dislodge it from Tucker (HOU) during the rebound.
Harden (HOU) briefly grasps and releases Aldridge's (SAS) jersey.
Harden (HOU) establishes himself in Murray's (SAS) path during the driving shot attempt and absorbs the contact.
Murray (SAS) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Harden (HOU) after the release of his jump shot attempt.
Aldridge (SAS) is late establishing himself in McLemore's (HOU) path and extends his lower body, delivering contact that affects McLemore's ability to defend.
White (SAS) maintains a legal guarding position on Westbrook (HOU) during the shot attempt.
Aldridge (SAS) is in the lane without actively guarding an opponent for longer than three seconds.
Westbrook (HOU) maintains a legal guarding position on White (SAS) during the drive.
Tucker (HOU) makes marginal contact with Gay (SAS) that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Murray (SAS) jumps toward Harden (HOU) and delivers contact to his body that affects his ability to follow-through naturally during his jump shot attempt.
Capela (HOU) makes marginal contact with Aldridge (SAS) as he is already under the basket and doesn't affect his ability to get to the long rebound.
Gay (SAS) commits a take foul on Harden (HOU).
Murray (SAS) commits a take foul on Harden (HOU).
Aldridge (SAS) sets the screen on McLemore (HOU) and does not deliver contact.
Aldridge (SAS) and McLemore (HOU) briefly engage and separate during the rebound.
Murray (SAS) makes marginal contact with Westbrook (HOU) after he has already lost control of the pass from Capela (HOU).
